    <section id="id1172641171756">
      <title>Learning Objectives</title>
      <para id="id1172636254004">With 100% accuracy during a: memory building activity, exercises, lab assignment, problems, or timed quiz/exam; the student is expected to:</para>
      <list id="id1172638651458" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>Define the terms on the definitions as listed in the modules associated with this chapter.</item>
        <item>Be able to list the categories and give examples of errors encountered when using an Integrated Development Environment (IDE).</item>
        <item>Write the C++ code for a program using appropriate planning documentation that you or another has designed.</item>
      </list>
