        <section id="fs-id1172638376324">
          <title>Problem 05b – Instructions</title>
          <para id="fs-id1172637825955"> Identify four (4) problems with this code listing (HINT: The four (4) types of errors encountered in a program using an Integrated Development Environment software product).</para>
